## ğŸ§© Project Workflow

1. User uploads a CSV file.
2. JavaScript reads the file using FileReader API.
3. CSV data is parsed into rows and columns.
4. Data is displayed in table format.
5. Statistics are calculated automatically.
6. Graph is generated using Chart.js.
7. Results appear on the dashboard.

---

## ğŸ§± Project Modules

### 1ï¸âƒ£ CSV Upload Module
- Select and upload CSV file.
- Reads file directly in browser.

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Data Parsing Module
- Splits CSV rows and columns.
- Cleans extra spaces.
- Converts numeric values properly.

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Table Display Module
- Generates table dynamically.
- Displays all records automatically.

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Score & Statistics Module
Calculates:
- Total records
- Average salary (score)
- Highest salary

### 5ï¸âƒ£ Graph Visualization Module
- Generates bar chart.
- Shows data levels clearly.
- Updates when new file is uploaded.

